{"title":"闪电（外二首）","authors":["刘佑局"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":10,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪电（外二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘佑局"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有雷声的高谈阔论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没有和风细雨的蜜语甜言；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命的火猛烈一击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把天地照得通红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！闪电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭示了一条人生哲理："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁可活一秒去照亮世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不愿在阴暗的角落苟活万年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瀑布"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇云崖奋然一跃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挟雷电光耀日月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是大海绷紧生命之弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进击的歌永不停歇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小溪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有江河澎湃的激情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没湖泊迷人的秋波；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜奔忙着寻找干渴的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地却献给她鲜花和甜果。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}